      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Neuroscience              : An introduction to how nerve cells generate action potentials, communicate with one another at synapses, develop synaptic connections, early brain development, and the construction of specific neural circuits.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Edward Ruthazer, Keith Murai, David Stellwagen (Fall)                  </p>

    
