                <h4>A. Cell and Molecular Stream</h4>

    
              <p>15 credits selected as follows:</p>
    
      
      
                <h4></h4>

    
              <p>9 credits as follows:</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/bioc-311" class="program-course-title">
